            <title>黄金商场通告指媒体「乱衰」声誉，未经许可下不准拍摄 + 将加紧巡视</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/21/shooting-work-is-not-allowed-in-golden-computer-arcade/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=shooting-work-is-not-allowed-in-golden-computer-arcade</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/21/shooting-work-is-not-allowed-in-golden-computer-arcade/hottopic/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 08:52:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活娱乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[黄金电脑商场]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1244951</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">黄金电脑商场近日被发现在场内张贴通告，重申商场内一向禁止所有未经许可的拍摄工作。通告中指出有媒体未经许可在商场内拍摄，并发布针对性的照片和报道。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244984" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_1208-466x580.jpg" alt="黄金电脑商场不准拍摄工作通告" width="466" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_1208-466x580.jpg 466w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_1208.jpg 540w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 466px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3723201/page/1">LIHKG</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1244982 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718959184-694x519.jpg" alt="黄金电脑商场" width="694" height="519" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718959184-694x519.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718959184.jpg 1203w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.freeguider.com/hk/venues/Golden-computer-arcade-disable-shopping">Free Guider</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">早在三个星期前本台就曾经到场内拍摄，更与场内 4 间电脑店舖的代表进行访谈，讨论俗称为「脑场」的黄金电脑商场的发展。访谈以「脑场」文化和香港砌机业的兴衰为主题。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_16868"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HxwBEsC6eys?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">黄金商场张贴的通告，将人流冷清、多个空置舖位的问题归究于媒体的恶意报道和唱衰，使商场的声誉受到损害。黄金电脑商场呼吁场内人士一旦发现未经许可的拍摄请立即通知管理处，并将会安排保安加紧场内的巡视工作。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3723201/page/1">LIHKG</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/21/shooting-work-is-not-allowed-in-golden-computer-arcade/hottopic/">黄金商场通告指媒体「乱衰」声誉，未经许可下不准拍摄 + 将加紧巡视</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
